sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant SPA as Angular SPA
    participant PF as PingFederate AS
    participant RS as Spring Boot RS
    participant PDP as PingAuthorize (PDP)
    participant Core as Core Banking API

    User->>SPA: Initiate payment transfer
    SPA->>PF: GET /as/authorize?authorization_details=[{type:banking_transfer,...}]
    PF->>User: Display login form
    User->>PF: Submit credentials

    PF->>PF: Issue token (no business validation)
    PF->>SPA: Redirect with auth_code
    SPA->>PF: POST /as/token.oauth2 (code)
    PF-->>SPA: access_token (JWT with authorization_details)

    SPA->>RS: POST /api/payments (Bearer token)
    RS->>RS: Validate JWT

    RS->>PF: POST /as/token.oauth2 (client_credentials)
    PF-->>RS: access_token (RS identity)

    RS->>PDP: POST /decisionEndpoints/{id} (actionId, ibanAccount, amount, groups)
    PDP->>Core: GET /api/users/{uid}/status
    Core-->>PDP: { blocked: false }
    PDP->>Core: GET /api/ibans/{iban}/status
    Core-->>PDP: { frozen: false }

    alt PDP permits
        PDP-->>RS: { decision: "PERMIT" }
        RS-->>SPA: 200 OK
    else PDP denies
        PDP-->>RS: { decision: "DENY", advice: "IBAN_FROZEN" }
        RS-->>SPA: 403 Forbidden
        SPA->>User: Display denial reason
    end
